node.title: Homes evacuated after vegetation fire breaks out in Northland
node.description: Fire crews are still at the scene.
node.content: ["A fire that broke out in Ahipara, Northland last night has been contained, Fire and Emergency said.\u00a0", "Six properties were evacuated after the fire spread to around three hectares Fire and Emergency District Manager Wipari Henwood said.\u00a0\n", "Local Northland brigades are still on the scene and helicopters are on standby, but residents are expected to be able to return to their homes today once the crews have finished at the scene.\u00a0\u00a0\n", "\u00a0"]
